&lt;li&gt;Assist Program and Project Managers with acquisition planning, procurement timelines, milestone tracking, and performance management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support preparation and development of acquisition documentation, acquisition plans, and program-related deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide assessments and recommendations throughout the acquisition lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
