&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop Statements of Work (SOWs), Statements of Objectives (SOOs), Performance Work Statements (PWSs), and other acquisition-related documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all acquisition documentation complies with USACE, FAA, GSA, CBP, HSAR, FAR, and applicable federal regulations and policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with stakeholders to gather requirements and prepare procurement-ready documentation for Government review and submission.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
