&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct market research and support the preparation of Determination of Findings and Analysis of Alternatives (AoA) documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and evaluate a minimum of three vendors capable of meeting program requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze vendor capabilities, pricing structures, and industry trends to support acquisition decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
